OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779120673
OL,3,CBlue Flags awarded to six beaches
OL,4,Cacross Bournemouth, Christchurch and
OL,5,CPoole
OL,7,FBeaches across Bournemouth,
OL,8,FChristchurch and Poole have retained
OL,9,Ftheir Blue Flag status.
OL,11,FKeep Britain Tidy awarded the
OL,12,Fdesignation to six beaches in the
OL,13,Farea, including Sandbanks, Highcliffe
OL,14,FBeach and Canford Cliffs.
OL,16,FA further three have received Seaside
OL,17,FAwards. They are Bournemouth, Boscombe
OL,18,Fand Avon Beach.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
