PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779120673
OL,3,CBlue Flags awarded to six beaches
OL,4,Cacross Bournemouth, Christchurch and
OL,5,CPoole
OL,7,FAvon Beach, however, does not have a
OL,8,FBlue Flag this year because of what
OL,9,FBournemouth, Christchurch and Poole
OL,10,F(BCP) Council called an
OL,11,F"administrative error".
OL,13,FThe award reflects a globally
OL,14,Frecognised standard for high water
OL,15,Fquality, environmental management,
OL,16,Fsafety and visitor services.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
