FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779120673
OL,3,CBlue Flags awarded to six beaches
OL,4,Cacross Bournemouth, Christchurch and
OL,5,CPoole
OL,7,FBCP Council praised its seafront teams
OL,8,Ffor the "consistently high standards
OL,9,Fdelivered throughout the year".
OL,11,FCouncillor Richard Herrett, Portfolio
OL,12,FHolder for Destination, Leisure, and
OL,13,FCommercial Operations at BCP Council,
OL,14,Fsaid: "While awards are important
OL,15,Frecognition, what matters most is the
OL,16,Fquality of the experience on our
OL,17,Fbeaches, which we are committed to
OL,18,Fmaintaining across all locations.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
