PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779120673
OL,3,CBlue Flags awarded to six beaches
OL,4,Cacross Bournemouth, Christchurch and
OL,5,CPoole
OL,7,F"I'd like to thank all of our
OL,8,Fstakeholders and partners that help
OL,9,Fmaintain our coastline, and
OL,10,Fparticularly the sponsors of the flags
OL,11,Fand awards that allow us to continue
OL,12,Fto showcase the work.
OL,14,F"We will continue to work with
OL,15,Fpartners to ensure our coastline
OL,16,Fremains one of the best in the
OL,17,Fcountry."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
