PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779120673
OL,3,CBlue Flags awarded to six beaches
OL,4,Cacross Bournemouth, Christchurch and
OL,5,CPoole
OL,7,FAddressing the lack of Blue Flag
OL,8,Fstatus for Avon Beach, the authority
OL,9,Fsaid "its appeal and its excellence
OL,10,Fgoes far beyond any single
OL,11,Faccreditation".
OL,13,FIn a statement, it added: "Avon
OL,14,FBeach's well-maintained promenades,
OL,15,Fthoughtfully managed facilities and
OL,16,Fvibrant mix of cafes, kiosks and
OL,17,Famenities - including a popular beach
OL,18,Fsauna and The Noisy Lobster restaurant
OL,19,F- will continue to draw people to
OL,20,FChristchurch Bay."
